{"tid":795091,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"因為今屆港姐同女朋友嗌交，點好？","createTime":"2018-08-26T17:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T17:19:53.000Z","uid":4790,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad7183a67a30cf852b861b91f1c95b868392792","tid":795091,"uid":4790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"另外兩個一個中文都講唔正（訓咗冇睇，唔知佢鬼妹仔定大陸妹），矮嗰個咁肉酸唔討論，咁個冠軍算係咁啦（除左棚牙），點都好過上屆呀下話？跟住就出事啦。原來我女人覺得佢好柒，話佢呃晒班男人咁話，我話個排名＂算係咁＂即係讚個冠軍靚，同佢持相反意見唔支持佢喎。無啦啦俾人開火屌左一鑊，我又屌返佢幾句咁樣，而家自己一個鳩fingfing訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁個冠軍係靚呀嘛，你條女唔撚抵得，聽日買禮物氹返佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都戇鳩，冠軍邊忽靚？買兩份禮物氹返佢啦<br />\n<br />\n利申　剩係睇咗宣佈賽果嗰幾分鐘，唔好屌我睇ｔｖｂ<br />\n<br />\n訓唔著求安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補圖　左邊係冠軍　好似係<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180826/_2018082621131573786.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180826%2F_2018082621131573786.jpg&h=2c36463c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a32ab504154bc2e33c77cea0374f4fa2f83c4842","tid":795091,"uid":4790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:07:38.000Z","msg":"好地地又俾人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日六點半起身呀　屌完我佢就訓得安樂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55c1e4df2ec85f884d255318409772b32edcaa9","tid":795091,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"飛"},{"pid":"fad6e3e0f94977665227e8ec77421219b8d56ca3","tid":795091,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"港姐靚唔靚都唔關你事，你女朋友心情唔靚你就好大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no